Lines.Line: You look like you could use some ordinance.
Ahh, I see more of my kind!
@p was your name, right? C'mon over and I'll get you strapped up.
Good to see you, @p. You interested in seeing some of my firepower?
You messed with the wrong Arms Dealer!
Ever heard of Delta Force? Those are who I roll with!
I knew this... day would come...
You want shit blown up? Well you came to the right place.
You got the dough I got the... uhh... damage? Is that a good word?
I'm packing heat. And it's my job to make sure you're packing it too!
Did you know? 6 out of every 10 colonists carry a gun. And it's my job to make sure the other 4 get their fair share.
Bring on the next big thing.
Bring on the next big thing.
Bring on the next big thing.
